Dhu ’l-Nûn on his travels is accosted by a majnûna (mad woman
devotee). ‘Dost thou know what generosity is?’ she asks him.

‘It is to give.’

‘In this world, no doubt. But in religion, what is generosity?’

‘It is to be instant to obey the Creator of the worlds.
